    "audio_latency": "CRITICAL: Preload audio or use OscillatorNode. Do not stream audio files on click."
  },
  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "1. Setup: Install 'framer-motion' and 'lucide-react' if not present.",
    "2. State Machine: Implement a robust state machine (IDLE -> WAITING -> READY -> FINISHED -> EARLY_CLICK).",
    "3. Latency: Ensure the 'Green' timestamp is captured immediately before the DOM update to account for render lag, or use performance.now() correctly.",
    "4. Mobile: Ensure the 'touch-action: manipulation' CSS property is set to prevent double-tap zoom delay.",
    "5. Result Logic: Sort the comparisons. Insert the user's score into the list dynamically.",
    "6. Visuals: Use the provided image URLs in circular avatars next to the bar charts.",
    "7. Accessibility: Ensure keyboard (Spacebar) can also trigger the reaction.",
    "8. Fun Factor: Add a random 'quip' message based on the score (e.g. 'Are you a robot?', 'Wake up!')."
  ],
  "universal_guidelines": [
    "Dark colors look good when used independently without gradients. DO NOT use dark colors as gradients.",
    "Don't make generic centered layouts, simplistic gradients, and uniform styling.",
    "Create depth through layered design elements with z-index hierarchy.",
    "Use glass-morphism effects with backdrop filters (12-24px blur).",
    "You MUST NOT apply universal transition. Eg: transition: all. This results in breaking transforms.",
